Renaissance Capital Hires Noluthando Ndebele as Sub-Sahara Research Head

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-05-04T07:35:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-04/renaissance-capital-hires-noluthando-ndebele-as-sub-sahara-research-head.html
Renaissance Capital  hired Nothando
Ndebele as head of sub-Saharan African research, it said in an
e-mailed statement today.  Ndebele most recently served as a senior investment officer
at Africap Microfinance Investment Co. in Johannesburg,
according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  